🔥 Production Scenario

Problem: Jenkins is down after a server reboot.

Investigation
systemctl status jenkins

journalctl -u jenkins

systemctl is-enabled jenkins

If disabled:

sudo systemctl enable jenkins
sudo systemctl start jenkins

Verify:

systemctl status jenkins
